class=\"item-credits\">Justin Sullivan</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Pinterest (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PINS\" title=\"Pinterest, Inc.\">PINS</a></span>) is quickly becoming a \u201ccash cow\u201d but the market has not taken notice. Investors appear razor-focused on the potential for decelerating top-line growth as the company begins to lap tough comparables. Yet the company appears to be on the cusp of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1141519003/image_1141519003.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743436-pinterest-is-a-strong-buy-with-gaap-inflection-around-the-corner", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 02:12:02"}, {"id": "4743435", "title": "Haleon: Guidance Implies Uncertainty Around Flu Season", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sensodyne Toothpaste Box in Hebrew\" data-id=\"477735211\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/477735211/image_477735211.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://stat